@startuml
participant "SparX Service" as Service
participant "Kafka" as Kafka
participant "Wonko" as Wonko
participant "Prometheus" as Prometheus
participant "PagerDuty" as PagerDuty

Service -> Kafka: Publish event
Kafka -> Wonko: Consume event
activate Wonko

Wonko -> Wonko: Process event
Wonko -> Wonko: Create/Update metrics

alt Alert condition met
    Wonko -> PagerDuty: Send alert
end

Prometheus -> Wonko: Scrape metrics
Wonko --> Prometheus: Return metrics

deactivate Wonko
@enduml